{"tid":1003277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"準新娘車禍後每天都失憶 男不離棄每天讓你重新愛一次","createTime":"2019-01-31T13:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:03:22.000Z","uid":212399,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5619033453a4aea13c6842978f4d5ef9c54cd9d","tid":1003277,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3877/d3877693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3877%2Fd3877693.jpg&h=6b076731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲丸山與立花祐也在這座主題樂園內約會，最後在這裡情訂終生。(圖／翻攝自YouTube)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n日本熊本縣一名25歲準新娘丸山，5個月前不幸發生車禍。出院後她每天醒來時都會像「電腦重設」一樣，忘掉之前所有事情。<br />\n然而準新郎立花祐也依然不離不棄，很有耐性的每天向她重新介紹自己，幫助她重建兩人交往兩年半以來的所有記憶，仿如電影《我們的50次初吻》的真實版。<br />\n丸山最後終於被感動，日前獲電視台一個實境秀郎目贊助，在東京一個主題樂園飯店內的教堂讓她向男方重新求婚，播出後感動一大票網友。<br />\n本月14日，電視台播出盛妝的丸山在教堂裡說：「我們可以再次在一起嗎？」，立花果斷回答說：「當然！」就在這一刻，許多網友們都說，他(她)們被感動到「眼睛都哭腫了」。<br />\n丸山選在這座主題樂園內向立花求婚，是因為她記起兩年前二人曾在這裡約會。為怕病發時又忘記一切，丸山特地把所有對男方感激的話統統寫在紙上，在求婚現場逐一唸出來。<br />\n儘管丸山記億「每天重新設定」的病能否痊癒，連醫生也不表示樂觀，但立花受訪時表示：願意永遠保護她，相伴偕老。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3877/d3877692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3877%2Fd3877692.jpg&h=a7ad67af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲穿上婚紗的丸山。(圖／翻攝自YouTube)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YQV1BPDQ6yQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYQV1BPDQ6yQ&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=a15543a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YQV1BPDQ6yQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qj6n1JyB7E8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqj6n1JyB7E8&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=8563a41b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qj6n1JyB7E8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190131/1369773.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190131%2F1369773.htm&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FZmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=d1edb5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190131/1369773.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f5bd2d44ce85f41e127cf8a1ae07c64036a730c1","tid":1003277,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61532d231270ff63664446c4392c3f2c6470bbbd","tid":1003277,"uid":109086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"一週的朋友真人版  又係每次都會自我介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9110acd3613237703a422b5225a1e5bd153fcefb","tid":1003277,"uid":13545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"50 first dates"},{"pid":"bb7aa329b1ef05d390184ffe0272e7d4aa27f868","tid":1003277,"uid":21204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}